This is THE FIRST RELEASE of MaliceRAT.
MaliceRAT is a REMOTE ACCESS TOOL (RAT) that enables attackers to gain unauthorized access to a victim's computer. It can be used to steal sensitive information, install malware, and carry out malicious activities.
It is IMPORTANT to TAKE PRECAUTIONS to PROTECT yourself from RATs like MaliceRAT. This includes keeping your software up to date, using strong passwords, and being cautious of suspicious emails and websites.
If you suspect that your computer has been infected with MaliceRAT or any other RAT, it is IMPORTANT to SEEK HELP from a cybersecurity professional to remove the malware and secure your system.
Stay SAFE online and BE VIGILANT against cyber threats like MaliceRAT.
